---
layout: base
title: Publications
description: Peer-reviewed and forthcoming publications by Mert Biricik in cybersecurity, memory forensics, BCI, and critical infrastructure protection.
priority: 0.8
changefreq: monthly
---

<section class="section pt-16 lg:pt-20">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <p class="section-eyebrow">Research</p>
    <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-ink-900 dark:text-white">Publications</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-ink-600 dark:text-ink-300">
      Peer-reviewed work and active manuscripts across cybersecurity, memory forensics, brain-computer interfaces, and AI-driven protection of critical infrastructure.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-ink-500 dark:text-ink-400">
      <a href="{{ metadata.social.scholar }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-700 hover:text-brand-800 dark:text-brand-300">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-graduation-cap"></i> View on Google Scholar
        <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square text-xs"></i>
      </a>
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 space-y-6">
      {% for pub in publications %}
      <article class="card-flat border-l-4 border-l-brand-500">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
          <span class="chip-brand">{{ pub.year }}</span>
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-700 dark:text-ink-200">{{ pub.venue }}</span>
          {% if pub.status == 'published' %}<span class="ml-auto inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-emerald-800 dark:bg-emerald-900/30 dark:text-emerald-300"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span>Published</span>{% endif %}
          {% if pub.status == 'under-review' %}<span class="ml-auto inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-100 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-amber-800 dark:bg-amber-900/30 dark:text-amber-300"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-500"></span>Under review</span>{% endif %}
          {% if pub.status == 'ready' %}<span class="ml-auto inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full bg-sky-100 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-sky-800 dark:bg-sky-900/30 dark:text-sky-300"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-sky-500"></span>Ready for submission</span>{% endif %}
          {% if pub.status == 'in-preparation' %}<span class="ml-auto inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full bg-ink-100 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-ink-700 dark:bg-ink-800 dark:text-ink-300"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-ink-500"></span>In preparation</span>{% endif %}
        </div>

        <h2 class="mt-4 text-xl font-semibold text-ink-900 dark:text-white">{{ pub.title }}</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm italic text-ink-500 dark:text-ink-400">{{ pub.authors | join(', ') }}</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-ink-700 dark:text-ink-300">{{ pub.summary }}</p>

        {% if pub.tags %}
        <ul class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {% for t in pub.tags %}<li class="chip">{{ t }}</li>{% endfor %}
        </ul>
        {% endif %}

        {% if pub.link %}
        <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2 pt-4 border-t border-ink-200 dark:border-ink-800">
          <a href="{{ pub.link }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-outline btn-sm">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-link"></i> DOI: {{ pub.doi }}
          </a>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section bg-ink-50 dark:bg-ink-900/40">
  <div class="container-wide">
    <p class="section-eyebrow">Research areas</p>
    <h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold text-ink-900 dark:text-white">What I research</h2>

    <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="inline-flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-50 text-brand-700 dark:bg-brand-900/40 dark:text-brand-300"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i></div>
        <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold">Critical infrastructure security</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-600 dark:text-ink-400">SCADA threat discovery, OSINT-based assessments, anomaly detection in power distribution networks.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="inline-flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-50 text-brand-700 dark:bg-brand-900/40 dark:text-brand-300"><i class="fa-solid fa-microchip"></i></div>
        <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold">Memory forensics</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-600 dark:text-ink-400">Unsupervised triage on Volatility3 artefacts; behavioural and graph-theoretic features against fileless malware.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="inline-flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-50 text-brand-700 dark:bg-brand-900/40 dark:text-brand-300"><i class="fa-solid fa-wave-square"></i></div>
        <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold">EEG / BCI signal processing</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-600 dark:text-ink-400">Real-time change-point detection (PELT) for asynchronous BCI on edge devices.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container-narrow text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-ink-900 dark:text-white">Research collaboration?</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-ink-600 dark:text-ink-300 max-w-xl mx-auto">Especially interested in joint work bridging applied cybersecurity, anomaly detection, and edge AI.</p>
    <div class="mt-7 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn-primary"><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i> Reach out</a>
      <a href="/projects/" class="btn-outline"><i class="fa-solid fa-folder-open"></i> Related projects</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
